column1:
After analyzing the daily new COVID-19 case counts from March to May 2020, we compiled a ranking of states based on how often each state appears in the daily top five increases. The state that ranks fourth overall is Illinois.

Here are the top five counties in Illinois based on their frequency of appearing in the daily top five new case counts:

county_name,frequency
Cook,92
Lake,80
DuPage,77
Kane,73
Will,63
